<br>
As far as the sash, I don't know a PC on it. It SHOULD be less than 2k since FBSS's go for 2-3k now and the Swiftclaw has less haste. The only problem is that Swiftclaws aren't sold all that often (at least on The Rathe) because of the work required to get one.<br>
<br>
As far as the weapon, I would replace the smoldering brand with a CoT or maybe Knuckle Dusters. You can get another CoT for 300-400, and may be able to get some KD's for about 1k. Another option is to go to Maiden's Eye and politely obtain a Goranga Spiked Club... That's free.<br>
