<br>
Spore Covered Armour may give you a better overall AC if you replaced your Wu stuff.  Each piece has 1 AC more than Wu and, whilst you'll lower your AGI by using it, you'll gain additional stat boosts and should get an overall higher AC (somebody with an in-depth knowledge of the AGI AC bonus modifier may be able to confirm this?  I certainly got a better AC when I did it)<br>
<br>
I'd also get a Lockjaw Hide Vest.  AC 12, 5 STA.  Personally, I wore one of them well into my 30's.<br>
<br>
If you've the cash, I'd replace your rings with 2 ac 6, 65 hp ones - should come to about 800pp or so for a pair (jewelers usually give a &quot;bulk buy&quot; discount if you buy two off them)<br>
<br>
I'd stick with the CoT.  I love this weapon and think it's deeply underrated.  It's not flashy, it doesn't proc anything but it's a &quot;constant worker.&quot;  I've only recently stopped using it (and I'm 49).<br>
<br>
Finally, on Saryrn the FBSS goes for 2-3k depending on seller.  I sold mine for 2.5k and had a couple of &quot;no thanks&quot;'s before eventually getting the asking price.  It just requires patience.  However, at 19 I wouldn't worry too much about a Haste item.  Looking at your profile, I'd be looking more into HP/Sta items.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps.<br>
<br>
